Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回去回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每次回来\N这里的时候就只会吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  让她走掉行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关我啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  犬夜叉那个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为担心他的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会阻止打斗的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打消念头嘛  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉吃醋不是家常便饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的心胸太狭窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会把钢牙的蠢话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他是个对自己\N毫无自信的可怜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也代表着他是真的喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是回去拿些药跟绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对犬夜叉要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也该让他担心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第47话\N奈落残留的鬼蜘蛛灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这么敏锐  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不只今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不下数次\N来查探我的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很在意我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你会在意我\N也是身不由己的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在你心中\N鬼蜘蛛的心还强烈的残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要先用餐  还是先洗澡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈现在就去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  好了  行李放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像是母亲和女儿的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是在外地就职的\N上班族与妻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  这次要待几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡个觉就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  草太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把绷带跟外伤药拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是床最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他稍微担心一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你会在意我\N也是身不由己的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在你心中\N鬼蜘蛛的心还强烈的残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明随时都可以杀了那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是因为我奈落的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留着对桔梗朝思暮想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个卑微的盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使身体无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对桔梗的非分之想却与日俱增
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后将身体献给众多的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而诞生出我奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那愚蠢人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对桔梗朝思暮想的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留在我奈落的身体里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你真是太轻视我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奈落不是鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在四魂之玉\N已大致到手的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心也等于无了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那团乌云是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才就停在寺院上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很不吉利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些光是…死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在吞噬着死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是奈落所做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘  您要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  马借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙打算吞尽\N这块土地所有的死魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让他得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  死魂被抽出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师  伤口的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是拜珊瑚\N你们的照顾所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  奈落还有着\N各式各样的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指兽郎丸和影郎丸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…第四个分身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟兽郎丸  只拥有战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落的命令都不服从
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那只是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却毫不犹豫砍下\N己方奈落的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落都难以掌控的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜伏在兽郎丸肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伺机攻击的哥哥影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样非常残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是完全不知底细的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后不知会出现怎样的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后非得要更加谨慎小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不打算\N去接戈薇姑娘回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不在我还乐的清静咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你不要把气氛\N搞的这么烦躁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真耐得住性子跟犬夜叉交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深表认同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是回去拿些药跟绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对犬夜叉要保密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也该让他担心一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和戈薇约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致上  怎么看\N都是钢牙的单相思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不用提心吊胆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闷不做声而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像全部都是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会道歉咧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇那个大浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是不快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不就变成大坏蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做了什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真的生气了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的死魂虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好严重的伤  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的毒蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是奈落搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算解决桔梗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不允许这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能让奈落杀害桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  我马上解决怪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这边静静等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大怪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上我算你倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有死魂\N你就无法存活了吗…桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要问你呢  你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被妖怪赶来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以来这里找我帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自负了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不知不觉中逃到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经晚上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不把我叫起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没睡醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你在想什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得\N我们和五十年前一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从将你封印在此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们因奈落的陷阱而彼此憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被封印在\N这棵树的五十年之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  那么是我变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我知道奈落\N那家伙的存在之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确曾经恨过你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  你不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追根究底  你也和奈落一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和奈落一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实残留着鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个盗贼一直\N希望我成为他的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地指使我亲手除掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是受盗贼鬼蜘蛛\N强烈的嫉妒心驱使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒…为了那么一点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就这么点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…这就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的体内\N还残留着鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说奈落对你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我似乎还残留着思念这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了否定这种念头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才想要我消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的体内已充满了死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一个人消灭奈落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那奈落居然迷恋着你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心至极
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的脑袋也该冷静了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉跟桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从奈落手中保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我而已不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在发什么疯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会杀了奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不需要再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人真是愚蠢的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为紧紧抱着  女人就是自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到现在的你就更能了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要奈落仍有鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定能趁虚而入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时正是净化奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他从世上完全消失掉的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾纠缠在一起的命运之线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法复元了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是鬼蜘蛛那龌龊人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姐姐在这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…他一直注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何…你目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,何不把真正重要的事物以外{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 都舍弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.67,0:25:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下定决心保护桔梗的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.91,0:25:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法留在他身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.47,0:25:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想的我  再度逃回了现代
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.68,0:25:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是四魂碎片还在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.21,0:25:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此非得回战国时代才行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.45,0:25:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还给犬夜叉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.32,0:25:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就真的结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.79,0:25:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦恼的我  站在第一次\N遇见犬夜叉的神木之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.99,0:25:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回到相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.48,0:25:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.83,0:26:39.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬死魂的妖怪{\pos(290,291)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:26:39.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落为了消灭\N桔梗而派来出来的{\pos(270,438)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:26:40.80,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大死魂虫{\pos(464,189)}
